,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:46:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我次次都做得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解可以做得返 你唔怕自己/對方仲留戀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍過3次拖 有2次都係散左個陣有啲老尷 但最後都frd返<br />\n剩低嗰陣就老尷左好耐到到依家都仲好老尷 不過都算做返frd掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有句嘢好撚老土但好中：<br />\n分手後仲做到朋友，一係就冇真正愛過；一係就仲仍然愛緊對方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7746cbc71e11f2b6bb0afed009f04fea8e390367","tid":166190,"uid":87955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:41:50.000Z","msg":"其實都要睇咩原因分手嘅<br />\n如果係性格不合淡左嗰d我認為做得返<br />\n如果係出軌打對方傷害過嗰d好難做得返"},{"pid":"438d3e21eac715ee77a4881c238a91b54fcbbb0c","tid":166190,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T08:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都要睇咩原因分手嘅<br />\n如果係性格不合淡左嗰d我認為做得返<br />\n如果係出軌打對方傷害過嗰d好難做得返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後者但對方聯絡翻我咁又點計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359b65bd7fbc80aa52cd93bc97814a346b7d492d","tid":166190,"uid":19933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我次次都做得返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解可以做得返 你唔怕自己/對方仲留戀咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拍過3次拖 有2次都係散左個陣有啲老尷 但最後都frd返<br />\n剩低嗰陣就老尷左好耐到到依家都仲好老尷 不過都算做返frd掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有句嘢好撚老土但好中：<br />\n分手後仲做到朋友，<span style=\"color: red;\">一係就冇真正愛過；一係就仲仍然愛緊對方</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj